WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.120
it's really important to know yourself internally

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:07.200
what you think you're capable of doing, right?

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:10.480
So yes, you have to convince someone else to hire you

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:12.960
that you're capable of doing what you say,

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:14.920
but you also have to know that.

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:18.080
And so I think once you are comfortable with that,

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.719
it makes it, you know,

00:00:19.719 --> 00:00:22.480
then you don't fear as much the unknown

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:24.840
of what the new job is going to look like.

